Spanish La Liga 2020-09-26 Alaves vs Getafe
match.strDescriptionEN: A Getafe arrives in Vitoria-Gasteiz determined to surprise everyone, as in past seasons.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-09-26 Betis vs Real Madrid
match.strDescriptionEN: After a bad start against Real Sociedad, Real Madrid is called upon to return to winning so as not to lose any more ground. How will it end against Betis?

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-09-26 Valencia vs Huesca
match.strDescriptionEN: After the defeat against Celta Vigo, Valencia immediately want to raise their heads. Will he succeed against the newly promoted Huesca?

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-09-26 Elche vs Sociedad
match.strDescriptionEN: Having stopped Real Madrid, Real Sociedad want a win against newly promoted Elche to seek valuable points.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-09-27 Ath Madrid vs Granada
match.strDescriptionEN: A lot of anticipation for Atlético Madrid's debut in the league. Simeone's team hosts Granada: the Andalusians are in great shape, and after the victory at home against Alavés they don't want to stop.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-09-27 Barcelona vs Villarreal
match.strDescriptionEN: Great expectations for the return of Barcelona to the Camp Nou: Villarreal are guests, for a game that promises to be full of possible twists.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-09-27 Eibar vs Ath Bilbao
match.strDescriptionEN: On the third day of the Liga the Eibar hosts the Athletic Club, for an all-Basque derby.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-09-27 Cadiz vs Sevilla
match.strDescriptionEN: Sevilla's championship begins with a derby against Cadiz. Lopetegui's team begins its season after the success in the Europa League last month: another championship to consolidate at the top and, why not, try to undermine the hegemony of Real and Barcelona.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-09-27 Osasuna vs Levante
match.strDescriptionEN: The Levante returns to the field after two weeks. Objective: redeem the defeat at the debut in the derby against Valencia. Complicated to do it on the Osasuna field, in the first home match of the season.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-09-27 Valladolid vs Celta Vigo
match.strDescriptionEN: Opposite starts for Valladolid and Celta. Only one point in two games for the hosts; four, however, for guests. Two trends all to be confirmed, given that we are only on the third day.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-09-29 Getafe vs Betis
match.strDescriptionEN: The defeat with Real Madrid at the last breath certainly does not take away the merit at the start of the Betis championship. Above all, it did not take away the primacy of the Andalusians, who lead the league table. A record that is difficult to maintain on a field like that of Getafe, a difficult and insidious opponent within friendly walls.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-09-29 Sociedad vs Valencia
match.strDescriptionEN: After the first victory against Elche, Real Sociedad aims to find continuity. He will try against Valencia, fresh from the home draw against Huesca.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-09-30 Eibar vs Elche
match.strDescriptionEN: After a bitter home defeat in the Basque derby against Athletic Bilbao, Eibar seeks redemption against newly promoted Elche. It will be a direct challenge, perhaps already decisive for establishing the hierarchies at the bottom of the ranking.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-09-30 Huesca vs Ath Madrid
match.strDescriptionEN: There is no rest for Atletico Madrid. After the seasonal debut against Granada, Simeone's team immediately returned to the field to face the newly promoted Huesca, a bit limping in this start to the championship.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-09-30 Real Madrid vs Valladolid
match.strDescriptionEN: After two consecutive away games, the first home for defending champion Real Madrid arrives. With the Santiago Bernabeu still not available, the venue for the match against Valladolid will be Valdebebas' Alfredo Di Stefano.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-09-30 Villarreal vs Alaves
match.strDescriptionEN: Dopo il netto 4-0 subito al Camp Nou, il Villarreal vuole rialzare la testa. Appuntamento all'Estadio de la Ceramica per una partita che il "Submarino Amarillo" non vuole sbagliare.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-01 Ath Bilbao vs Cadiz
match.strDescriptionEN: A win and a defeat so far in the league for Athletic Bilbao and Cadiz. The Basques want to start their season at San Mamés with a win, will they succeed?

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-01 Celta Vigo vs Barcelona
match.strDescriptionEN: Second engagement in a few days for Barcelona, who opened their league by receiving Villarreal and now travels to Vigo to face Celta. A field that closely resembles a taboo for the Blaugrana, who have not won here since 2015 and who threw away a piece of the last Liga in Balaídos.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-01 Sevilla vs Levante
match.strDescriptionEN: Three points each for Sevilla and Levante, with the difference that the Andalusians have only played one game in this Liga. Will Paco Lopez's team be able to ruin Rakitic and his team mates' season debut at Sánchez Pizjuán?

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2021-01-12 Granada vs Osasuna
Spanish La Liga 2020-10-03 Ath Madrid vs Villarreal
match.strDescriptionEN: After scoring in his seasonal debut at Wanda Metropolitano, Simeone wants to continue to keep the production level of his incredible attack high. On the other hand, there is a Villarreal that has started a new project with Unai Emery and does not want to repeat the fool of the Camp Nou.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-03 Sociedad vs Getafe
match.strDescriptionEN: Real Sociedad is one of the teams to have played, with ups and downs, in all four days of this Liga. Back to back at the Anoeta: after hosting Valencia, Getafe arrives.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-03 Valencia vs Betis
Spanish La Liga 2020-10-03 Valladolid vs Eibar
match.strDescriptionEN: Difficult start at home for Ronaldo's team, the phenomenon who is looking for their first home victory of the season against Eibar.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-03 Elche vs Huesca
match.strDescriptionEN: The newly promoted Elche, after the heavy debut defeat against Real Sociedad, is trying to give the first points at home to its fans. Huesca arrives in Valencia for what can already be called a direct battle for salvation.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-04 Alaves vs Ath Bilbao
match.strDescriptionEN: Less than an hour's drive separates Vitoria-Gasteiz from Bilbao: it is a significant match both from a historical and a sporting point of view. In fact, Alavés and Athletic are playing important points.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-04 Barcelona vs Sevilla
match.strDescriptionEN: Barcelona returns to Camp Nou, where in the last meeting they have trimmed 4 goals at Villarreal. Lopetegui's Sevilla opponent of the day, with a game that promises to be anything but simple.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-04 Cadiz vs Granada
match.strDescriptionEN: The 6-1 defeat to Atlético may have repercussions on a Granada determined, however, to raise their heads as soon as possible. Appointment in Cadiz for a match not to be missed for Diego Martinez's men.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-04 Levante vs Real Madrid
match.strDescriptionEN: Appointment in Valencia for Zidane's Real Madrid. The reigning champions of the Spanish league are looking for the 3 points at Levante.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-04 Osasuna vs Celta Vigo
match.strDescriptionEN: After having saved with a lot of trouble in the past Liga, Celta Vigo tries to put together peace of mind right away. In Pamplona he will find an Osasuna who instead wants to repeat the excellent 2019/20 championship.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-17 Celta Vigo vs Ath Madrid
match.strDescriptionEN: A mixed start to the season for Atletico: the 6-1 in the debut against Granada, with the Suarez show, had given good hope, but then two consecutive draws arrived. The break was used to recharge the batteries and put order to start again in a big way, starting with the trip against Celta Vigo, back from two KOs in a match before the break.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-17 Getafe vs Barcelona
match.strDescriptionEN: After the draw against Sevilla and the break, Barcelona are back on the pitch to face Getafe. The blaugrana chase Real Madrid at three points, albeit with one game less and above all, with Clásico just seven days away.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-17 Granada vs Sevilla
match.strDescriptionEN: Granada and Sevilla resume after the break with the Andalusian derby. The hosts are returning from a defeat, sound against Atletico, and a draw, after two consecutive victories; the guests, on the other hand, are still unbeaten, albeit with one game less, and came out unscathed from the Camp Nou, just before the break.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-17 Real Madrid vs Cadiz
match.strDescriptionEN: LaLiga is back and Real Madrid is back on the pitch, already at the top of the standings even with one game less. It is the beginning of an important week for the Blancos, with the debut in the Champions League and the Clásico, so watch out for traps: Cadiz is ready to exploit the slightest misstep of Zidane's men.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-18 Alaves vs Elche
match.strDescriptionEN: Four points each for Alavés and Elche who find themselves fighting in the lower parts of the standings.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-18 Ath Bilbao vs Levante
match.strDescriptionEN: A worrying start to the championship for Levante and Athletic Bilbao, who, after four games played, find themselves in the relegation zone. The Basques are still looking for their first home win, will they be able to find the three points against the Valencia team?

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-18 Betis vs Sociedad
match.strDescriptionEN: An excellent start has taken Betis to the top positions of the league, and now the green-and-white people of Seville are asking their players to look for other heavy points to dream big. Appointment at Benito Villamarin to see if Real Sociedad will be able to stop the ambitions of the Andalusians.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-18 Eibar vs Osasuna
match.strDescriptionEN: After three consecutive defeats, Eibar managed to find their first championship victory. Jonathan Calleri's Osasuna arrives in Ipurua.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-18 Huesca vs Valladolid
match.strDescriptionEN: Difficult start to the championship for a Valladolid who has not yet found their first success of the season. Will he be able to take home the first 3 points against newly promoted Huesca?

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-18 Villarreal vs Valencia
match.strDescriptionEN: Villarreal midfielder Dani Parejo finds his great love, Valencia, for the first time as an opponent. Captain with 282 appearances and 53 goals scored, a match with a unique emotional charge.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-23 Elche vs Valencia
Spanish La Liga 2020-10-24 Ath Madrid vs Betis
Spanish La Liga 2020-10-24 Barcelona vs Real Madrid
match.strDescriptionEN: As every time, it will be more than just a match: the Clasico between Real and Barça confronts the two superpowers of Spanish football.

match.strFilename: Spanish La Liga 2020-10-24 Osasuna vs Ath Bilbao
Spanish La Liga 2020-10-24 Sevilla vs Eibar

Spanish La Liga 2020-10-30 Eibar vs Cadiz
match.strDescriptionEN: The newly promoted Cadiz is taking away a lot of satisfaction in this La Liga start of the season. Already three victories, one of which is historic against Real Madrid in Valdebebas. There are other saving points at stake against Eibar.
